<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>IronScape Fitness</title>
  <meta name="description" content="IronScape is a gamified training system built around a simple idea: training should feel like progression — not just logging." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0a0c10;
      --panel: rgba(19, 23, 31, 0.84);
      --panel-2: rgba(25, 30, 40, 0.74);
      --text: #f3f5f7;
      --muted: #a9b1bc;
      --gold: #e1b24b;
      --gold-2: #c8942d;
      --line: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      --shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
      --radius: 22px;
      --max: 1180px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 0%, rgba(225,178,75,0.16), transparent 34%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 15%, rgba(70,98,146,0.16), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #090b0f 0%, #0d1117 35%, #0b0d12 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    .shell {
      width: min(100% - 32px, var(--max));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .nav {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 20;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      background: rgba(8, 10, 13, 0.7);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .nav-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 24px;
      padding: 16px 0;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    }

    .logo {
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 30% 25%, rgba(255,255,255,0.25), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(145deg, #1b2029 0%, #12161d 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(225,178,75,0.32);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.04), 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.96rem;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }

    .cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 13px 18px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(225,178,75,0.32);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(225,178,75,0.18), rgba(225,178,75,0.08));
      color: #fff3d3;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, border-color 0.18s ease, background 0.18s ease;
    }

    .cta:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      border-color: rgba(225,178,75,0.52);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(225,178,75,0.24), rgba(225,178,75,0.1));
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      padding: 72px 0 32px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 34px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: #f7d892;
      background: rgba(225,178,75,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(225,178,75,0.2);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.35rem, 6vw, 4.85rem);
      line-height: 0.96;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .hero p {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 60ch;
    }

    .hero-copy .actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 26px;
    }

    .ghost {
      padding: 13px 18px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero-card {
      position: relative;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(22,27,35,0.94), rgba(12,16,22,0.94));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
      min-height: 540px;
    }

    .hero-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 12%, rgba(225,178,75,0.18), transparent 28%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 72% 84%, rgba(42,88,158,0.15), transparent 28%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .phone {
      width: min(82%, 390px);
      margin: 28px auto;
      border-radius: 34px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #131820, #0d1117);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      padding: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
    }

    .screen {
      border-radius: 24px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0f141b 0%, #101820 100%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    .screen-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 18px 18px 10px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .screen-title {
      padding: 0 18px 14px;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .xp-bar {
      margin: 0 18px 16px;
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .xp-bar span {
      display: block;
      width: 68%;
      height: 100%;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold-2), var(--gold));
      border-radius: inherit;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 0 18px 18px;
    }

    .tile {
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), rgba(255,255,255,0.03));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    .tile .small {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .tile strong {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 28px 0 24px;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: end;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.65rem);
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .sub {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 66ch;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .feature-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .card {
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--panel), rgba(15,18,24,0.92));
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .icon {
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #f8d892;
      background: rgba(225,178,75,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(225,178,75,0.18);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 1.12rem;
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .split {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 18px;
    }

    .panel-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .panel-item {
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .panel-item span { color: var(--muted); }

    .muted-box {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .links {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .links a {
      display: block;
      padding: 22px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--panel-2), rgba(11,14,19,0.92));
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      transition: transform 0.18s ease, border-color 0.18s ease;
    }

    .links a:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      border-color: rgba(225,178,75,0.24);
    }

    .links strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .links span {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      display: block;
    }

    footer {
      padding: 36px 0 58px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .footer-wrap {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding-top: 22px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .feature-grid,
      .split,
      .links {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hero { padding-top: 44px; }
      .hero-card { min-height: auto; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .shell { width: min(100% - 20px, var(--max)); }
      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .section-head { align-items: start; }
      h1 { font-size: 2.35rem; }
      .brand span:last-child { display: none; }
      .nav-inner { gap: 12px; }
      .cta, .ghost { width: 100%; }
      .hero-copy .actions { flex-direction: column; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="shell nav-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="#top" aria-label="IronScape Fitness home">
        <div class="logo">⚔</div>
        <span>IronScape Fitness</span>
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#features">Features</a>
        <a href="#support">Support</a>
        <a href="#privacy">Privacy</a>
      </div>
      <a class="cta" href="https://apps.apple.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Download on the App Store</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main id="top">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="shell hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy">
          <div class="eyebrow">Level up your training</div>
          <h1>Training should feel like progression — not just logging.</h1>
          <p>
            IronScape is a gamified training system built around a simple idea: your workouts should feel more like building a character and less like filling out a spreadsheet. Log real training, earn XP, level up muscle groups, and manage fatigue over time.
          </p>
          <div class="actions">
            <a class="cta" href="https://apps.apple.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Get IronScape</a>
            <a class="ghost" href="#features">See features</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="phone">
            <div class="screen">
              <div class="screen-top">
                <span>IronScape</span>
                <span>Lv. 27</span>
              </div>
              <div class="screen-title">Skills Overview</div>
              <div class="xp-bar"><span></span></div>
              <div class="grid">
                <div class="tile">
                  <div class="small">Skill</div>
                  <strong>Chest</strong>
                  <div>Level 18</div>
                </div>
                <div class="tile">
                  <div class="small">Skill</div>
                  <strong>Back</strong>
                  <div>Level 15</div>
                </div>
                <div class="tile">
                  <div class="small">Skill</div>
                  <strong>Quads</strong>
                  <div>Level 14</div>
                </div>
                <div class="tile">
                  <div class="small">Skill</div>
                  <strong>Cardio</strong>
                  <div>Level 11</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="about">
      <div class="shell">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>About IronScape</h2>
            <p class="sub">
              IronScape blends workout logging, progression systems, and an RPG-inspired aesthetic into a single fitness experience. The goal is simple: make consistent training feel rewarding.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="split">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="icon">✦</div>
            <h3>Built for progression</h3>
            <p>
              Most fitness apps store data. IronScape turns that data into a progression loop. Train muscle groups, accumulate XP, build your profile, and keep pushing forward.
            </p>
            <div class="panel-list">
              <div class="panel-item"><strong>Skill XP</strong><span>Earn from real workouts</span></div>
              <div class="panel-item"><strong>Fatigue</strong><span>Manage recovery and load</span></div>
              <div class="panel-item"><strong>Nutrition</strong><span>Track meals and macros</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div class="icon">⚙</div>
            <h3>Simple support site structure</h3>
            <p>
              This GitHub Pages version is designed to cover the essentials for your live app presence: a clean landing page, support access, privacy information, and a polished brand-forward presentation.
            </p>
            <div class="muted-box">
              Replace the App Store link, logo, screenshots, and policy copy with your live IronScape assets. Because GitHub Pages serves static files, this setup is lightweight, fast, and cheap to maintain.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="features">
      <div class="shell">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>Core features</h2>
            <p class="sub">A structure that mirrors the public-facing messaging already associated with IronScape Fitness.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-grid">
          <article class="card">
            <div class="icon">⬆</div>
            <h3>Muscle-based skill system</h3>
            <p>Train specific muscle groups and build a profile that develops over time, like a character build shaped by your actual training.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <div class="icon">⌁</div>
            <h3>Fatigue-aware progression</h3>
            <p>Push hard, recover intelligently, and avoid turning every workout into a brute-force grind with no regard for recovery.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <div class="icon">◫</div>
            <h3>Workout logging + builder</h3>
            <p>Track sets, reps, weight, and effort while building reusable routines that match your training style.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <div class="icon">◔</div>
            <h3>Nutrition tracking</h3>
            <p>Log meals, calories, and macros so nutrition sits beside training instead of living in a completely separate workflow.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <div class="icon">▣</div>
            <h3>Dark RPG aesthetic</h3>
            <p>A visual identity designed to feel distinct from generic fitness dashboards, with a mood closer to progression than bookkeeping.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <div class="icon">↗</div>
            <h3>Progress dashboard</h3>
            <p>See how skills, training load, and consistency evolve over time so every session feels like it moves the needle.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="support">
      <div class="shell">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <h2>Support & policy links</h2>
            <p class="sub">Use these sections to preserve the same practical structure your current support website appears to have.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="links">
          <a href="mailto:support@ironscapefitness.com">
            <strong>Support</strong>
            <span>Contact the IronScape support team for help with app questions, issues, or general assistance.</span>
          </a>
          <a id="privacy" href="#privacy-copy">
            <strong>Privacy Policy</strong>
            <span>Explain how IronScape handles data, what is collected, and how users can reach you with privacy questions.</span>
          </a>
          <a href="#about">
            <strong>About IronScape</strong>
            <span>Share the product mission, progression philosophy, and the app’s RPG-inspired training approach.</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="privacy-copy">
      <div class="shell">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="section-head" style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
            <div>
              <h2>Privacy policy placeholder</h2>
              <p class="sub">Paste your current approved policy text here so the GitHub Pages site can fully replace the old hosted version.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="muted-box">
            <strong style="display:block; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 12px;">Suggested structure</strong>
            Include sections for information collected, how data is used, third-party services, data retention, security, children’s privacy, and contact details. If your current live site already has policy copy you want preserved exactly, replace this block with that final text.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <div class="shell footer-wrap">
      <div>© <span id="year"></span> IronScape Fitness. All rights reserved.</div>
      <div>support@ironscapefitness.com</div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script>
    document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
  </script>
</body>
</html>
